But that means there'll be
two of you, permanently.

532
00:32:20,600 --> 00:32:21,600
RORY: Forever.

533
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:23,360
FUTURE AMY:
And that way we both get to live.

534
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:25,320
Two Amys together. Can that work?

535
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:27,160
I don't know. It's your marriage.

536
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:28,440
Doctor!

537
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:33,720
Perhaps, maybe if I shunted
the reality compensators on the Tardis,

538
00:32:33,800 --> 00:32:38,040
we calibrated the doomsday pumpers
and jettison the karaoke bar, yes,

539
00:32:38,360 --> 00:32:39,680
maybe, yes.

540
00:32:41,280 --> 00:32:43,840
It could do it.
The Tardis could sustain the paradox.

541
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:45,240
RORY: Right.

542
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:47,000
Army.

543
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:51,400
And Amy.

544
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:56,760
The wife and the wife. Right.

545
00:32:58,280 --> 00:33:01,200
Okay, Amy, Past Amy, stand by the door.
Future Amy, you, too.

546
00:33:01,280 --> 00:33:02,920
Future Amy, can I borrow
your sonic screw...

547
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:04,520
It's a probe.

548
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:06,080
It's a screwdriver.

549
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:08,440
DOCTOR: Rory, sonic at double-out power.

550
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:10,000
Amy now, you're our link to Amy then.

551
00:33:10,080 --> 00:33:12,600
We need to get a signal through
and that signal will be a thought.

552
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:14,720
Amy now and Amy then, share a thought.

553
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:17,960
Something so powerful
that it can rip through time.

554
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:19,400
Rory, sonic the pin front.

555
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:22,360
Inside you will find three levers
and a jumble of wire.

556
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:23,640
That's the regulator valve.

557
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:26,400
After we reroute it, you'll have
10 minutes to get back to the Tardis.

558
00:33:26,480 --> 00:33:28,120
-Okay.
-Pull out the red and green receptors.

559
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:30,560
Reroute blue into the red
and the green into the blue.

560
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:33,560
Leave the red loose,
and on no account touch anything yellow.

561
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:36,840
Come on, Rory,
it's hardly rocket science.

562
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,960
It's just quantum physics.

563
00:33:39,040 --> 00:33:43,760
Yes, right. Okay, blue into red.
Red into...

564
00:33:43,840 --> 00:33:45,440
Now the levers, throw them in order.

565
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:48,000
And Amy, start thinking the most
important thought you have ever had.

566
00:33:48,080 --> 00:33:49,960
Hold it in your head
and do not let it go.

567
00:33:51,640 --> 00:33:52,720
Lever one.

568
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:56,440
-Macarena.
-Macarena.

569
00:33:57,320 --> 00:33:58,800
-Macarena.
-Macarena.

570
00:33:59,840 --> 00:34:01,120
She's doing the Macarena.

571
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:03,040
-Macarena.
-Macarena.

572
00:34:03,480 --> 00:34:04,760
Macarena!

573
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:07,240
-Our first kiss.
-Lever two, Rory.

574
00:34:15,480 --> 00:34:16,560
Lever three!

575
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:29,040
Oh, Amy!

576
00:34:32,200 --> 00:34:34,280
-Oh, my God!
-Oh, my God!

577
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:44,400
(LAUGHING)

578
00:34:45,200 --> 00:34:46,920
Yeah. Sorry.

579
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,320
-Hello.
-Hello.

580
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:59,600
-I don't know what...
-I don't know what...

581
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:00,800
Weird.

582
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:03,200
-Okay, this is weird.
-Okay, this is weird.

583
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:06,240
-Right, just stop doing that.
-Right, just stop doing that.

584
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:08,480
How about, Amy 1 speaks first?

585
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:09,880
-Which one's Amy 1?
-Which one's Amy 1?

586
00:35:09,960 --> 00:35:11,040
Well, you...

587
00:35:11,120 --> 00:35:12,480
-I am
-I am.

588
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,560
-No, I am.
-No, I am.

589
00:35:14,640 --> 00:35:15,680
-Rory!
-Rory!

590
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:17,400
-Rory, just stop doing that.
-Rory, just stop doing that.

591
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,560
Ah!

592
00:35:18,640 --> 00:35:21,800
Rory, Rory, take the glasses off.
You'll get temporal feedback.

593
00:35:23,200 --> 00:35:25,000
Whoa! Calm down there, Rory.

594
00:35:25,240 --> 00:35:28,880
Amy, we've created a massive paradox
and the Tardis hates it.

595
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:31,200
Trying to get out of here.

596
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:34,560
What's the nasty Amy done to you?

597
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:36,760
Just calm down there.
Hang on in there, eh?

598
00:35:38,160 --> 00:35:40,800
Rory, you've got eight minutes left.

599
00:35:41,040 --> 00:35:42,640
I'm sorry, you're on your own now.

600
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:55,520
I'm not on my own.

601
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,880
I've got my wives.

602
00:35:58,880 --> 00:36:00,480
HANDBOT: Do not be alarmed.
RORY: They're coming!

