00:36:00,560 --> 00:36:02,160
This is a kindness.

604
00:36:02,240 --> 00:36:04,400
-With me.
-Do not be alarmed.

605
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:06,200
This is a kindness.

606
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:08,520
-This is a kindness.
-Amy.

607
00:36:08,600 --> 00:36:10,920
-Deactivate.
-Kate Hatter. Year 10 hockey.

608
