AMY: So you think you're going to
come with us, just like that?

615
00:36:28,560 --> 00:36:29,960
FUTURE AMY: Yeah, just like that.

616
00:36:30,040 --> 00:36:31,880
-Rory, talk to her.
-Rory, talk to her.

617
00:36:31,960 --> 00:36:33,160
Now, ladies.

618
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:35,440
AMY: Where are you going to live?

619
00:36:35,520 --> 00:36:36,880
FUTURE AMY:
Not with you, don't worry.

620
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:38,200
I'll go travelling.

621
